<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>أوربِت — منصة الألعاب</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Almarai:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg-0:#060a1f;
    --bg-1:#0b1230;
    --bg-2:#121a42;
    --panel:#141c47;
    --panel-hover:#1a2456;
    --line: rgba(140,160,255,0.14);
    --cyan:#3fd3ff;
    --violet:#7c6bff;
    --gold:#ffc84a;
    --text-0:#f2f4ff;
    --text-1:#aab3e0;
    --text-2:#6f78a8;
  }

  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}

  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}

  body{
    background:var(--bg-0);
    color:var(--text-0);
    font-family:'Tajawal', 'Almarai', sans-serif;
    overflow-x:hidden;
  }

  ::selection{background:var(--violet); color:#fff;}

  a{color:inherit; text-decoration:none;}

  button{font-family:inherit; cursor:pointer; border:none;}

  /* ===== Background ambience ===== */
  body::before{
    content:"";
    position:fixed; inset:0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(60% 45% at 82% -5%, rgba(124,107,255,0.20), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(50% 40% at 10% 10%, rgba(63,211,255,0.14), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events:none;
    z-index:0;
  }

  /* ===== Nav ===== */
  header{
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50;
    background:rgba(6,10,31,0.75);
    backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .nav-wrap{
    max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:16px 28px;
  }
  .logo{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    font-weight:900; font-size:1.35rem; letter-spacing:0.5px;
  }
  .logo-mark{
    width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:10px;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet));
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-size:1.1rem; box-shadow:0 0 22px rgba(63,211,255,0.45);
  }
  nav ul{
    display:flex; gap:32px; list-style:none;
  }
  nav ul li a{
    color:var(--text-1); font-weight:500; font-size:0.95rem;
    transition:color .2s;
    position:relative;
  }
  nav ul li a:hover{color:var(--text-0);}
  nav ul li a::after{
    content:""; position:absolute; right:0; bottom:-8px; width:0; height:2px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--cyan),var(--violet));
    transition:width .25s;
  }
  nav ul li a:hover::after{width:100%;}
  .nav-cta{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet));
    color:#04081c; font-weight:800; font-size:0.9rem;
    padding:10px 22px; border-radius:999px;
  }
  .nav-links-desktop{display:flex;}
  @media (max-width:820px){
    .nav-links-desktop{display:none;}
  }

  /* ===== Hero with starfield ===== */
  .hero{
    position:relative;
    max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto;
    padding:90px 28px 70px;
    text-align:center;
    z-index:1;
  }
  #starfield{
    position:absolute; inset:0;
    top:-20px;
    z-index:0;
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    color:var(--cyan); font-weight:700; font-size:0.85rem;
    background:rgba(63,211,255,0.08);
    border:1px solid rgba(63,211,255,0.3);
    padding:7px 16px; border-radius:999px;
    margin-bottom:26px;
  }
  .hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
    font-weight:900; line-height:1.25;
    margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .hero h1 span{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet));
    -webkit-background-clip:text; background-clip:text; color:transparent;
  }
  .hero p{
    color:var(--text-1); font-size:1.05rem; max-width:560px;
    margin:0 auto 34px; line-height:1.9;
  }
  .hero-actions{display:flex; gap:16px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .btn-primary{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet));
    color:#04081c; font-weight:800; font-size:1rem;
    padding:15px 34px; border-radius:14px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 30px -8px rgba(124,107,255,0.55);
    transition:transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px); box-shadow:0 14px 36px -6px rgba(124,107,255,0.7);}
  .btn-ghost{
    color:var(--text-0); font-weight:700; font-size:1rem;
    padding:15px 30px; border-radius:14px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    transition:background .2s, border-color .2s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-color:rgba(140,160,255,0.35);}

  .stat-row{
    display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:56px;
    margin-top:64px; flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .stat-item{text-align:center;}
  .stat-item b{font-size:1.9rem; font-weight:900; display:block;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet));
    -webkit-background-clip:text; background-clip:text; color:transparent;}
  .stat-item span{color:var(--text-2); font-size:0.85rem;}

  /* ===== Section heading ===== */
  .section{max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:60px 28px; position:relative; z-index:1;}
  .section-head{
    display:flex; align-items:flex-end; justify-content:space-between;
    margin-bottom:34px; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:18px;
  }
  .section-head h2{font-size:1.9rem; font-weight:900;}
  .section-head p{color:var(--text-2); font-size:0.95rem; margin-top:6px;}

  /* ===== Filter tabs ===== */
  .filters{
    display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:34px;
  }
  .filter-btn{
    background:var(--panel); color:var(--text-1);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:9px 20px; border-radius:999px; font-size:0.88rem; font-weight:700;
    transition:all .2s;
  }
  .filter-btn:hover{color:var(--text-0); border-color:rgba(140,160,255,0.4);}
  .filter-btn.active{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet));
    color:#04081c; border-color:transparent;
  }

  /* ===== Game grid ===== */
  .grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(270px, 1fr));
    gap:22px;
  }
  .card{
    background:linear-gradient(180deg, var(--panel), var(--bg-1));
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:20px;
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px;
    transition:transform .25s, border-color .25s, box-shadow .25s;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .card::before{
    content:""; position:absolute; inset:0; opacity:0;
    background:radial-gradient(120% 100% at 50% 0%, rgba(124,107,255,0.16), transparent 60%);
    transition:opacity .25s;
  }
  .card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-6px);
    border-color:rgba(140,160,255,0.35);
    box-shadow:0 18px 40px -18px rgba(20,30,90,0.7);
  }
  .card:hover::before{opacity:1;}

  .card-top{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px;}
  .icon-tile{
    width:64px; height:64px; min-width:64px; border-radius:16px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-size:1.9rem;
    box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .card h3{font-size:1.12rem; font-weight:800;}
  .tag{
    display:inline-block; margin-top:4px;
    font-size:0.72rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--text-2);
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:3px 10px; border-radius:999px;
  }

  .rating-row{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;}
  .stars{display:flex; gap:2px; position:relative;}
  .star{width:16px; height:16px; color:#33395e;}
  .star svg{width:100%; height:100%; display:block;}
  .star.filled{color:var(--gold);}
  .star.half{position:relative; color:#33395e;}
  .star.half .fill{
    position:absolute; inset:0; overflow:hidden; width:50%; color:var(--gold);
  }
  .rating-num{font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--text-1); font-weight:700;}
  .rating-count{font-size:0.78rem; color:var(--text-2);}

  .card-meta{
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
    font-size:0.78rem; color:var(--text-2);
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    padding-top:12px;
  }

  .install-btn{
    margin-top:2px;
    width:100%;
    background:var(--panel-hover);
    border:1px solid rgba(140,160,255,0.25);
    color:var(--text-0);
    font-weight:800; font-size:0.92rem;
    padding:12px; border-radius:12px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px;
    transition:background .25s, box-shadow .25s, border-color .25s, color .25s;
  }
  .install-btn svg{width:16px; height:16px;}
  .install-btn:hover{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet));
    color:#04081c;
    border-color:transparent;
    box-shadow:0 10px 24px -8px rgba(63,211,255,0.5);
  }
  .install-btn.installed{
    background:rgba(63,211,255,0.08);
    color:var(--cyan);
    border-color:rgba(63,211,255,0.35);
  }

  /* ===== Footer ===== */
  footer{
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    margin-top:40px;
    padding:44px 28px 30px;
    position:relative; z-index:1;
  }
  .footer-wrap{
    max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto;
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
    flex-wrap:wrap; gap:20px;
  }
  .footer-wrap p{color:var(--text-2); font-size:0.85rem;}
  .footer-links{display:flex; gap:22px;}
  .footer-links a{color:var(--text-2); font-size:0.85rem; transition:color .2s;}
  .footer-links a:hover{color:var(--text-0);}

  @media (max-width:600px){
    .nav-wrap{padding:14px 18px;}
    .hero{padding:64px 18px 48px;}
    .section{padding:44px 18px;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="nav-wrap">
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="logo-mark">🚀</div>
      أوربِت
    </div>
    <nav class="nav-links-desktop">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#home">الرئيسية</a></li>
        <li><a href="#games">الألعاب</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" onclick="return false;">التصنيفات</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" onclick="return false;">الدعم</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <a href="#games" class="nav-cta">تصفح الآن</a>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero" id="home">
  <canvas id="starfield"></canvas>
  <div class="eyebrow">✨ أكثر من 40 مليون تنزيل حول العالم</div>
  <h1>عالمك القادم من <span>الألعاب</span><br>يبدأ من هنا</h1>
  <p>اكتشف أفضل الألعاب المُختارة بعناية، بتقييمات حقيقية من اللاعبين، وثبّتها في ثوانٍ معدودة بدون تعقيد.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#games" class="btn-primary">استكشف الألعاب</a>
    <a href="#" class="btn-ghost" onclick="return false;">شاهد العرض التقديمي</a>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-row">
    <div class="stat-item"><b>+120</b><span>لعبة مميزة</span></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><b>4.8</b><span>متوسط التقييم</span></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><b>+2M</b><span>لاعب نشط</span></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><b>24/7</b><span>دعم فني</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="games">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div>
      <h2>الألعاب المميزة</h2>
      <p>مُنتقاة يدويًا، ومُحدّثة أسبوعيًا</p>
    </div>
  </div>
